Our Mission

“To be the most preferred LSP by continuously adapting to the ever growing business environment through ethical business practices and strict adherence towards the effective QMS.”

OUR STRENGTHS

3 Decades of Experience in handling ODC and Heavy Equipment Transport

Milk Run

Milk Run services applied where the load is scattered in many different places and in smaller units. In such a case carrying from each centre individually would be very expensive, hence a scheme is designed as per the requirements and accordingly all different units .

Long Haul

Long Haul is the movement of cargo between two major cities. Star Roadline has the experience and the knowledge to help you with your long haul transportation needs.

Local Distrubution

Our local freight distribution system enables us to exactly match your local transportation and logistic needs, vehicles in various types engaged dedicatedly to serve our customers locally.

Part Load

Part load transport service in India, we capture every transportation route and meet your requirements. We provide full & part load transportation Services with varied type of trucks.

JIT Supplies

The just-in-time supply system is a management strategy that aligns raw-material orders from suppliers directly with production schedules. Companies use this strategy to increase efficiency with low inventory levels.

Local Distrubution

All our vehicles are GPS enabled for easy tracking. Our customer can track and trace the vehicles from their end as we share the access of our vehicle tracking system to them.
